<chapter id="icon-scheme">
  <title>Icon Naming Scheme</title>
  <para>
    Icons need to be present in tango style and in 16x16, 22x22, and svg versions.
  </para>

  <sect1 id="icon-indexes">
    <title>Icon indexes</title>
    <para>
      Indexes are ranges specified by the specification.
      A percentage scale is divided into 6 index groups:
    </para>
    <informaltable>
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Index</entry>
            <entry>Range</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>000</literal></entry>
            <entry>0%  - 10%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>020</literal></entry>
            <entry>11% - 30%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>040</literal></entry>
            <entry>31% - 50%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>060</literal></entry>
            <entry>51% - 70%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>080</literal></entry>
            <entry>71% - 90%</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>100</literal></entry>
            <entry>91% - 100%</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
    <para>
      A wireless device scale is divided into 4 csr groups:
    </para>
    <informaltable>
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Index</entry>
            <entry>Range</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>000</literal></entry>
            <entry>CSR0,CSR1</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>030</literal></entry>
            <entry>CSR2,CSR3</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>060</literal></entry>
            <entry>CSR4,CSR5</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry><literal>100</literal></entry>
            <entry>CSR6,CSR7</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
  </sect1>

  <sect1 id="icon-names">
    <title>Icon Names</title>
    <para>
      These are the icon names.
    </para>
    <informaltable>
      <tgroup cols="2">
